Paella:
- Arborio rice (or Spanish Bomba rice)
- Chicken pieces (thighs, drumsticks, etc.)
- Seafood (shrimp, mussels, squid, etc.)
- Sausage (chorizo or other Spanish sausage)
- Onion
- Bell peppers
- Tomatoes
- Garlic
- Saffron threads
- Paprika (smoked or sweet)
- Chicken or seafood broth
- Olive oil
- Lemon wedges
- Fresh parsley (chopped)
- Salt and pepper
